title: Criminally Under-viewed Youtubers
body:
I would like to hear what youtubers you guys think are criminally underviewed. I've been watching a TON of Lathrix (Lathland) and find his videos entertaining. He doesn't have a huge following but I think he should with the content volume and quality he produces. Even his older stuff is good.

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCFLXUteuWTuXIjxf2OpKC4A

Also in a more league related note, N3ac3y is amazing, good content, very educational, entertaining and I appreciate his videos

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC8CurliJrMFY5oX2FA9nsDA


What are some channels you think deserve way more attention than what they currently have? with so many content publishers, it is hard to sort the good from the bad :/


@ COMMANDO YI YO BRO, YOUR VIDEO JUST HIT MY HOME PAGE 

thats cool. your jungle guide is in the top line of my feed without ever clicking to your channel.
